# Color Palette & Theming

## ðŸŽ¨ Design Philosophy

MomentMoi embraces **sophisticated elegance** with **modern functionality**. The design should feel:

- **Sophisticated & Calming**: Clean lines, gentle shadows, refined typography with a calming teal accent
- **Modern & Minimalist**: Clean layouts, plenty of whitespace, contemporary design patterns
- **Accessible & Inclusive**: High contrast ratios, clear navigation, mobile-first approach
- **Professional & Trustworthy**: Subtle animations, thoughtful micro-interactions, sophisticated color palette

## ðŸŽ¯ Color Palette

### Primary Colors - Sophisticated Teal

```typescript
// Primary - Sophisticated Teal
primary: {
  50: '#f0f9f9',   // Lightest teal - backgrounds
  100: '#cceceb',  // Very light teal - hover states
  200: '#99d8d6',  // Light teal - borders, dividers
  300: '#66c4c1',  // Medium light teal - icons, accents
  400: '#5a9b99',  // Medium teal - secondary buttons
  500: '#507c7b',  // Main primary - primary buttons, links
  600: '#456a69',  // Deep teal - hover states
  700: '#3a5757',  // Dark teal - text on light backgrounds
  800: '#2f4545',  // Darker teal - headings
  900: '#243333'   // Darkest teal - body text
}
```

### Secondary Colors - Warm Accent

```typescript
// Secondary - Warm Accent
secondary: {
  50: '#faf9f7',   // Cream white - backgrounds
  100: '#f4f1ed',  // Light cream - hover states
  200: '#e8e1d9',  // Soft cream - borders
  300: '#dcd1c5',  // Medium cream - icons
  400: '#c5b8a8',  // Warm beige - secondary elements
  500: '#a89d8e',  // Main secondary - accents
  600: '#8b8075',  // Deep beige - text
  700: '#6e635c',  // Dark beige - headings
  800: '#514743',  // Darker brown - emphasis
  900: '#342a2a'   // Darkest brown - body text
}
```

### System Colors

```typescript
// System Colors - For backgrounds, text, and UI elements
background: '#f1f0ef',    // Main system background
surface: '#fafafa',       // Card elements background
border: '#eeeeee',        // Border color
text: {
  primary: '#212121',     // Main text color
  secondary: '#616161',   // Secondary text
  muted: '#9e9e9e'        // Muted text
}
```

### Extended Neutral Scale

```typescript
// Extended Neutral Scale
neutral: {
  50: '#fafafa',   // Lightest (matches card color)
  100: '#f5f5f5',  // Very light gray
  200: '#eeeeee',  // Light gray (matches border)
  300: '#e0e0e0',  // Soft gray
  400: '#bdbdbd',  // Medium gray
  500: '#9e9e9e',  // Gray
  600: '#757575',  // Dark gray
  700: '#616161',  // Darker gray
  800: '#424242',  // Very dark gray
  900: '#212121'   // Almost black (matches text)
}
```

